Dinner: Fried Radish Cake (Vegeterian) ⁣⁣
Ok recipe is up! Click link on bio and search "fried radish cake" or go to www.bit.ly/friedradish⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Its gluten free!⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Ingredients: daikon radish, carrot, garlic, green onions, eggs, rice flour, tapioca flour, salt, white pepper, avocado oil, maple sugar
I love this! Thank you for putting up the recipe
